title: Robotics in review: Editors look back at 2025
description:
The editorial team reviews 2025’s top robotics stories, including iRobot’s bankruptcy, the humanoid boom, and Waymo’s scaling.

The post Robotics in review: Editors look back at 2025 appeared first on The Robot Report.
